  "Destroying raw data after analysis is complete": "",
  "Keeping all methods secret from other researchers": "",
  "Never publishing research findings": "",
  "Reproducibility requires transparent reporting of methods and data so that other researchers can repeat the study and verify the findings independently.": "",
